  "body": {
    "view": {
      "representation": "view",
      "value": "<div class=\"contentLayout2\"><style>[data-colorid=xe7i7xenrx]{color:#3e3f40} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=xe7i7xenrx]{color:#bfc0c1}[data-colorid=mts4u7zetz]{color:#3e3f40} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=mts4u7zetz]{color:#bfc0c1}[data-colorid=gd0w4p8jxb]{color:#3e3f40} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=gd0w4p8jxb]{color:#bfc0c1}[data-colorid=ztrbeezxce]{color:#3e3f40} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=ztrbeezxce]{color:#bfc0c1}[data-colorid=nlzpgj992k]{color:#3e3f40} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=nlzpgj992k]{color:#bfc0c1}[data-colorid=i7vbv9x6ax]{color:#3e3f40} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=i7vbv9x6ax]{color:#bfc0c1}[data-colorid=ndw2sfhfjk]{color:#3e3f40} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=ndw2sfhfjk]{color:#bfc0c1}[data-colorid=oaz8fhd7kj]{color:#3e3f40} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=oaz8fhd7kj]{color:#bfc0c1}[data-colorid=mel1eurryq]{color:#3e3f40} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=mel1eurryq]{color:#bfc0c1}</style>\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542227805/meshLightAnimGlassHQ.gif?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330660501&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542227805/meshLightAnimGlassHQ.gif?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330660501&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"384\" data-width=\"384\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542227885\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"meshLightAnimGlassHQ.gif\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/gif\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542227805\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"123fec49-7a1f-414f-91d8-ed1e1d3d0802\" data-media-type=\"file\" /></span><p>PxrMeshLight allows you to create arbitrary shapes and use them as bonafide light sources. This improves performance over emissive geometry and provides great flexibility for creating things like neon lights, futuristic light panels, and deforming shapes that light a scene.</p><p>The parameters are simple and easy to tune and the light follows the shape's render visibility as opposed to selections on the light.</p><div class=\"confluence-information-macro confluence-information-macro-warning conf-macro output-block\" data-hasbody=\"true\" data-macro-id=\"4d262e3a-f4e2-4e4c-9613-f41295614d09\" data-macro-name=\"warning\"><span class=\"aui-icon aui-icon-small aui-iconfont-error confluence-information-macro-icon\"> </span><div class=\"confluence-information-macro-body\"><p>While you may use a meshlight as a deforming piece of geometry, deformation motion blur is not yet supported and could provide incorrect results.</p></div></div><div class=\"confluence-information-macro confluence-information-macro-information conf-macro output-block\" data-hasbody=\"true\" data-macro-id=\"3a79ff85-a6d7-498e-a0ea-79a4dda4a50e\" data-macro-name=\"info\"><span class=\"aui-icon aui-icon-small aui-iconfont-info confluence-information-macro-icon\"> </span><div class=\"confluence-information-macro-body\"><p>In creating a meshlight, you may see a material connected to it called PxrBlack. This material has no parameters and is designed to prevent the mesh from scattering light a second time from itself. This is done to provide something intuitive, not necessarily something physical.</p></div></div><p><br /></p><h3 id=\"PxrMeshLight-Parameters\">Parameters</h3><h4 id=\"PxrMeshLight-Basic\">Basic</h4><p><br /></p><p><strong>Color</strong></p><p><span data-colorid=\"ndw2sfhfjk\">The color of the emitted light.</span></p><p><span data-colorid=\"gd0w4p8jxb\"> </span></p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout three-equal\" data-layout=\"three-equal\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"pxrMeshLght_colorAqua.jpg\" width=\"384\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542227805/pxrMeshLght_colorAqua.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330660322&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542227805/pxrMeshLght_colorAqua.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330660322&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"384\" data-width=\"384\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542227876\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"pxrMeshLght_colorAqua.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542227805\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"c92a673a-641e-4ab1-93fa-38c846ec1ddd\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542227805/pxrMeshLght_colorAqua.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330660322&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542227805/pxrMeshLght_colorAqua.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330660322&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384 1x\" /></span></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"pxrMeshLght_colorGreen.jpg\" width=\"384\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542227805/pxrMeshLght_colorGreen.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330660321&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542227805/pxrMeshLght_colorGreen.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330660321&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"384\" data-width=\"384\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542227873\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"pxrMeshLght_colorGreen.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542227805\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"ad778575-e9bb-41b7-9e8f-c764960cd6eb\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542227805/pxrMeshLght_colorGreen.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330660321&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542227805/pxrMeshLght_colorGreen.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330660321&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384 1x\" /></span></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"pxrMeshLght_colorPurple.jpg\" width=\"384\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542227805/pxrMeshLght_colorPurple.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330660322&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542227805/pxrMeshLght_colorPurple.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330660322&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"384\" data-width=\"384\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542227879\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"pxrMeshLght_colorPurple.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542227805\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"2ff9f14e-bc8e-4b18-b60a-777767ec6d0f\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542227805/pxrMeshLght_colorPurple.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330660322&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542227805/pxrMeshLght_colorPurple.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330660322&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384 1x\" /></span></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<p><br /></p><p><strong>Intensity</strong></p><p>Scales the contribution of this light linearly. The light intensity is computed using physical falloff.</p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout three-equal\" data-layout=\"three-equal\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"pxrMeshLght_intensity05.jpg\" width=\"384\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542227805/pxrMeshLght_intensity05.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330660150&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542227805/pxrMeshLght_intensity05.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330660150&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"384\" data-width=\"384\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542227867\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"pxrMeshLght_intensity05.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542227805\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"a4decef6-7da6-4c3e-8816-75488d13b399\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542227805/pxrMeshLght_intensity05.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330660150&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542227805/pxrMeshLght_intensity05.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330660150&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384 1x\" /></span></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"pxrMeshLght_intensity10.jpg\" width=\"384\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542227805/pxrMeshLght_intensity10.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330660151&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542227805/pxrMeshLght_intensity10.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330660151&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"384\" data-width=\"384\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542227870\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"pxrMeshLght_intensity10.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542227805\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"9294dcc8-7a94-4a83-b55d-2c9e8ad089c9\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542227805/pxrMeshLght_intensity10.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330660151&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542227805/pxrMeshLght_intensity10.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330660151&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384 1x\" /></span></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"pxrMeshLght_intensity20.jpg\" width=\"384\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542227805/pxrMeshLght_intensity20.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330660150&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542227805/pxrMeshLght_intensity20.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330660150&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"384\" data-width=\"384\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542227864\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"pxrMeshLght_intensity20.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542227805\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"c6757c5b-72c7-41cf-b122-ba0652b01f23\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542227805/pxrMeshLght_intensity20.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330660150&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542227805/pxrMeshLght_intensity20.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330660150&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384 1x\" /></span></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<p><br /></p><p><strong>Exposure</strong></p><p><span data-colorid=\"oaz8fhd7kj\">Specifies the exposure of the area light as a power of 2. Increasing the exposure by 1 will double the energy emitted by the light source. A value of&nbsp;0&nbsp;produces an intensity of 1 at the source, -1 produces 0.5. R</span> <span data-colorid=\"xe7i7xenrx\">eal world lighting has high energies and typical exposures are low values while you may have to type a really large number for equivalent&nbsp;</span>Intensity<span data-colorid=\"mel1eurryq\">. This is also comfortable to artists familiar with photographic measurements.</span></p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout three-equal\" data-layout=\"three-equal\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"pxrMeshLght_exposure00.jpg\" width=\"384\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542227805/pxrMeshLght_exposure00.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330659973&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542227805/pxrMeshLght_exposure00.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330659973&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"384\" data-width=\"384\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542227858\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"pxrMeshLght_exposure00.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542227805\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"20b44e3b-b1d7-41c1-9608-c511f5b5e229\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542227805/pxrMeshLght_exposure00.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330659973&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542227805/pxrMeshLght_exposure00.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330659973&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384 1x\" /></span></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"pxrMeshLght_exposure02.jpg\" width=\"384\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542227805/pxrMeshLght_exposure02.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330659973&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542227805/pxrMeshLght_exposure02.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330659973&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"384\" data-width=\"384\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542227861\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"pxrMeshLght_exposure02.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542227805\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"03d0d620-ccf2-498b-a478-53ebd48f8209\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542227805/pxrMeshLght_exposure02.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330659973&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542227805/pxrMeshLght_exposure02.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330659973&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384 1x\" /></span></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"pxrMeshLght_exposure04.jpg\" width=\"384\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542227805/pxrMeshLght_exposure04.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330659973&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542227805/pxrMeshLght_exposure04.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330659973&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"384\" data-width=\"384\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542227855\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"pxrMeshLght_exposure04.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542227805\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"4a558aa9-773f-4bc9-a423-c5f5dadab322\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542227805/pxrMeshLght_exposure04.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330659973&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542227805/pxrMeshLght_exposure04.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330659973&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384 1x\" /></span></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<p><br /></p><p><strong>Texture Color</strong></p><p><span data-colorid=\"ztrbeezxce\">An image to use as a light source using a pattern node, e.g. </span><a href=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/REN27/pages/542225070/PxrTexture\" rel=\"nofollow\"><span data-colorid=\"mts4u7zetz\">PxrTexture</span></a><span data-colorid=\"nlzpgj992k\">. Preferably a High Dynamic Range source. Notice this affects color and shadowing based on the contents of the HDRI used. If forced to use an 8-bit source such as a JPEG image, it should be linearized (transformed to linear color space) before use as a color. Since this is indeed a mesh, you must have defined UVs or appropriate projections to place your texture correctly.</span></p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout three-equal\" data-layout=\"three-equal\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"pxrMeshLght_texColor1.jpg\" width=\"384\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542227805/pxrMeshLght_texColor1.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330659769&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.