 data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"pxrMeshLght_texColor2.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542227805\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"33d1c24e-88a6-4cf8-adbe-cf2af21f2d74\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542227805/pxrMeshLght_texColor2.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330659768&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542227805/pxrMeshLght_texColor2.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330659768&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384 1x\" /></span></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"pxrMeshLght_texColor3.jpg\" width=\"384\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542227805/pxrMeshLght_texColor3.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330659769&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542227805/pxrMeshLght_texColor3.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330659769&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"384\" data-width=\"384\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542227849\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"pxrMeshLght_texColor3.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542227805\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"c5c6e17c-e894-4d15-bc67-abbcc3b87385\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542227805/pxrMeshLght_texColor3.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330659769&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542227805/pxrMeshLght_texColor3.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330659769&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384 1x\" /></span></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<p><br /></p><p><strong>Enable Temperature</strong></p><p><span data-colorid=\"i7vbv9x6ax\">Turns color temperature on or off.</span></p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout three-equal\" data-layout=\"three-equal\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"pxrMeshLght_colorTemp3000.jpg\" width=\"384\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542227805/pxrMeshLght_colorTemp3000.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330659581&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542227805/pxrMeshLght_colorTemp3000.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330659581&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"384\" data-width=\"384\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542227837\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"pxrMeshLght_colorTemp3000.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542227805\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"e8fc8973-85ba-4ad2-8475-1c499ebedcc5\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542227805/pxrMeshLght_colorTemp3000.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330659581&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542227805/pxrMeshLght_colorTemp3000.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330659581&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384 1x\" /></span></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"pxrMeshLght_colorTemp6500.jpg\" width=\"384\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542227805/pxrMeshLght_colorTemp6500.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330659582&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542227805/pxrMeshLght_colorTemp6500.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330659582&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"384\" data-width=\"384\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542227843\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"pxrMeshLght_colorTemp6500.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542227805\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"233e1043-8440-4dce-90cc-d664a372a29a\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542227805/pxrMeshLght_colorTemp6500.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330659582&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542227805/pxrMeshLght_colorTemp6500.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330659582&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384 1x\" /></span></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"pxrMeshLght_colorTemp9000.jpg\" width=\"384\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542227805/pxrMeshLght_colorTemp9000.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330659582&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542227805/pxrMeshLght_colorTemp9000.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330659582&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"384\" data-width=\"384\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542227840\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"pxrMeshLght_colorTemp9000.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542227805\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"0f4fb6da-a026-48a6-b93f-fed7b625699e\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542227805/pxrMeshLght_colorTemp9000.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330659582&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542227805/pxrMeshLght_colorTemp9000.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330659582&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384 1x\" /></span></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<p><br /></p><p><strong>Temperature</strong></p><p>Allow the user to choose the&nbsp;color temperature&nbsp;of the light in&nbsp;Kelvins. Unlike the basic light color, this allows the user to easily pick plausible light colors based on standard temperature measurements.This control will act like a filter or gel (a tinted transparent surface) in front of your light. If your light is white, you will get the chosen color temperature. If your light is colored, the color temperature will make it cooler (over 6500K) or warmer (below 6500K).</p><p><br /></p><div class=\"confluence-information-macro confluence-information-macro-information conf-macro output-block\" data-hasbody=\"true\" data-macro-id=\"a99a67cb-dea3-49ce-b677-f6e2679c20f1\" data-macro-name=\"info\"><span class=\"aui-icon aui-icon-small aui-iconfont-info confluence-information-macro-icon\"> </span><div class=\"confluence-information-macro-body\"><p>The effect will be less pronounced on fully saturated mono-chromatic lights. Defaults to 6500K, which should be very close to white on most monitors (D65 illuminant used by sRGB and Rec 709).</p></div></div><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><hr /><h4 id=\"PxrMeshLight-Refine\">Refine</h4><p><br /></p><p><strong>Specular Amount</strong></p><p>Amount of specular light that is emitted.&nbsp;This is a non-physical control.&nbsp;You could use a light with&nbsp; <strong>Specular Amount</strong> &nbsp;0.0 to act purely as a source of diffuse light for your scene objects and avoid adding highlights.&nbsp;</p><p><br /></p><p><strong>Diffuse Amount</strong></p><p>Amount of diffuse light that is emitted. This is a non-physical control.&nbsp;You could use a light with&nbsp; <strong>Diffuse Amount</strong> &nbsp;0.0 to act purely as a source of highlights for your scene objects.</p><p><br /></p><p><strong>Intensity Near Dist</strong></p><p>Near distance between the point being illuminated and the light at which the sample doesn't get brighter. This may help you avoid hot spots and sampling issues where a light is near a surface. These values are based on your scene scale/distance so this is just an example.</p><p><br /></p><p><strong>Specular Near Dist</strong></p><p>Near distance between the point with specular shading being illuminated and the light at which the sample doesn't get brighter. This may help you avoid hot spots and sampling issues where a light is near a specular surface. <strong>Note</strong> that this value will not apply to lights as seen from the camera. <span class=\"legacy-color-text-default\">Below, the right sphere has a distance of 0.0, 5.0, and finally 10.0. These values are based on your scene scale/distance so this is just an example.</span></p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout three-equal\" data-layout=\"three-equal\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"pxrRectLght_SpecNearDist_00.jpg\" width=\"423\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542227805/pxrRectLght_SpecNearDist_00.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330659414&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=423&amp;height=423\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542227805/pxrRectLght_SpecNearDist_00.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330659414&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"77760\" data-width=\"77760\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542227831\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"pxrRectLght_SpecNearDist_00.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542227805\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"e4c2a4b1-9633-41fa-83ad-88307f812558\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542227805/pxrRectLght_SpecNearDist_00.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330659414&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=846&amp;height=846 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542227805/pxrRectLght_SpecNearDist_00.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330659414&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=423&amp;height=423 1x\" /></span></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"pxrRectLght_SpecNearDist_50.jpg\" width=\"423\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542227805/pxrRectLght_SpecNearDist_50.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330659413&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=423&amp;height=423\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542227805/pxrRectLght_SpecNearDist_50.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330659413&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"77760\" data-width=\"77760\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542227828\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"pxrRectLght_SpecNearDist_50.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542227805\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"8225a5f6-7f1d-4b83-808e-37da9263d971\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542227805/pxrRectLght_SpecNearDist_50.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330659413&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=846&amp;height=846 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542227805/pxrRectLght_SpecNearDist_50.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330659413&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=423&amp;height=423 1x\" /></span></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"pxrRectLght_SpecNearDist_100.jpg\" width=\"423\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542227805/pxrRectLght_SpecNearDist_100.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330659414&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=423&amp;height=423\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542227805/pxrRectLght_SpecNearDist_100.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330659414&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"77760\" data-width=\"77760\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542227834\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"pxrRectLght_SpecNearDist_100.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542227805\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"78da7b35-36ee-4fa4-b03d-28c1cd401c90\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542227805/pxrRectLght_SpecNearDist_100.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330659414&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=846&amp;height=846 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542227805/pxrRectLght_SpecNearDist_100.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330659414&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=423&amp;height=423 1x\" /></span></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<p><br /></p><p><strong>Diffuse Near Dist</strong></p><p>Near distance between the point with diffuse shading being illuminated and the light at which the sample doesn't get brighter. This may help you avoid hot spots and sampling issues where a light is near a diffuse surface. <strong>Note</strong> that this value will not apply to lights as seen from the camera. <span class=\"legacy-color-text-default\">Below, the left sphere has a distance of 0.0, 5.0, and finally 10.0. These values are based on your scene scale/distance so this is just an example.</span></p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout three-equal\" data-layout=\"three-equal\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"pxrRectLght_DiffNearDist_00.jpg\" width=\"423\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542227805/pxrRectLght_DiffNearDist_00.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330659187&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=423&amp;height=423\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542227805/pxrRectLght_DiffNearDist_00.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330659187&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"77760\" data-width=\"77760\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542227819\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"pxrRectLght_DiffNearDist_00.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542227805\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"91388024-9cd0-4f7e-8c08-3ef7e6b5623f\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542227805/pxrRectLght_DiffNearDist_00.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330659187&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=846&amp;height=846 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542227805/pxrRectLght_DiffNearDist_00.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330659187&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=423&amp;height=423 1x\" /></span></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"pxrRectLght_DiffNearDist_50.jpg\" width=\"423\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542227805/pxrRectLght_DiffNearDist_50.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330659187&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=423&amp;height=423\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542227805/pxrRectLght_DiffNearDist_50.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330659187&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"77760\" data-width=\"77760\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542227822\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"pxrRectLght_DiffNearDist_50.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542227805\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"b5ab439a-7d1c-401e-9300-abdbb3449bfd\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542227805/pxrRectLght_DiffNearDist_50.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330659187&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=846&amp;height=846 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542227805/pxrRectLght_DiffNearDist_50.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330659187&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=423&amp;height=423 1x\" /></span></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"pxrRectLght_DiffNearDist_100.jpg\" width=\"423\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542227805/pxrRectLght_DiffNearDist_100.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330659187&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=423&amp;height=423\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542227805/pxrRectLght_DiffNearDist_100.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330659187&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"77760\" data-width=\"77760\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542227825\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"pxrRectLght_DiffNearDist_100.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542227805\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"7446b699-5cd5-498a-8906-d14f89143ec9\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542227805/pxrRectLght_DiffNearDist_100.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330659187&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=846&amp;height=846 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542227805/pxrRectLght_DiffNearDist_100.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330659187&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=423&amp;height=423 1x\" /></span></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<p><br /></p><hr /><h4 id=\"PxrMeshLight-Advanced\">Advanced</h4><p><br /></p><p><strong>Area Normalize</strong></p><p>When normalize is enabled, the amount of light contributed to the scene will not change as you scale the light source. This makes it easier to adjust highlight size without changing scene lighting.</p><p><br /></p><p><strong>Trace Light Paths</strong></p><p>Enable light and photon tracing from this light. This value enforces a physically-based light and as a side-effect disables the above&nbsp;<strong>Shadows</strong>&nbsp;controls. Users may use this feature to selectively decide which lights emit photons when using the PxrVCM or PxrUnified Integrators.</p><p><br /></p><p><strong>Thin Shadow</strong></p><p>Enable thin shadow and disable refraction caustics for this light. This parameter will ignored if&nbsp;<strong>Trace Light Paths</strong>&nbsp;is enabled. This is a non-physical control that creates &quot;fake&quot; colored shadows for transmissive objects without needing to generate photons for caustics.</p><p><br /></p><p><strong>Light Group</strong></p><p>Specify the light group name used for light group LPEs. This is useful to generate per-light AOVs for later adjustment in compositing.</p><p><br /></p><p><strong>Importance Multiplier</strong></p><p>Rather than setting explicit Light Samples, users can change the amount of samples the light will be assigned internally by changing this value. RenderMan creates a set of samples at render time for all lights in the scene and changing this value rebalances the samples across the lights. Note that&nbsp;increasing&nbsp;this value will cause&nbsp;<em>more</em>&nbsp;samples to be selected from this light while reducing it for others in the scene. Lower than the default will&nbsp;<em>decrease</em>&nbsp;the samples while providing more to others in the scene.</p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>"
    }
